QuestData.Title: The Culmination of Our Efforts
QuestData.RewardText: With every day, more warriors arrive at Azshara's command. Soon, Neptulon the Tidehunter will hear of our preparations, but too late to stop what we have set in motion. Our numbers will be too great and our allies too powerful. Victory is only a matter of time.$B$BIn Azshara's name.
